title: clawq manifest teams CLI
---
CLI command: clawq manifest teams [--output FILE]
- Reads slash_commands.ml command list (sorted by priority)
- Takes top 10 (Teams limit) and outputs manifest JSON fragment
- Output format: bots.commandLists[].commands[] entries
- Can be piped or pasted into app manifest